question: Show me all central banks and commercial banks in the UK.
sql_query1:
SELECT Banks.Name 
FROM Banks
WHERE (Banks.types_of_bank = "Central Bank" OR Banks.types_of_bank = "Commercial Bank") AND Banks.country = "UK"
sql_query2:
SELECT Banks.Name 
FROM Banks
WHERE Banks.types_of_bank = "Central Bank" OR Banks.types_of_bank = "Commercial Bank" AND Banks.country = "UK"
interpretation1: Show both central and commercial banks based in the UK.
interpretation2: Show all the central banks, in addition show the UK-based commercial banks.
